### 3. Trust and Security Considerations
Due to running out of time, [Trust and Security Considerations](https://datatracker.ietf.org/meeting/126/materials/slides-126-sml-trust-and-security-considerations-00) for `draft-ietf-sml-trust` was not presented.

## Decisions and Action Items

### Decisions
*   **Plain-text support:** Officially dropped from `draft-ietf-sml-structured-quoted-content` to simplify implementation.
*   **Forward preamble:** Added to `draft-ietf-sml-structured-quoted-content`.

